productAttributes.productDescription: Combining Style with Color is what your Ochive Pocket Watch would give you. Wear it formally with your dinner jacket or tag it informally to your jeans - an ultimate style and fashion statement highlighting your young and modern sophistication. The Ochive is made in Italy by Full spot, designed by laboratories. The Ochive Pocket Watches are available in 10 attractive colors and are available with white face and 3 black hands including a seconds hand. It comes with a 40 cm white painted metal chain and clip which you can attach to your clothes, as jeans or waistcoat. The Watch can be closed with soft and tactile silicone cover.
